Trigger("Player 1"){
Conditions:
	Switch("Switch7", not set);

Actions:
	Preserve Trigger();
	Run AI Script("+Vi7");
	Set Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Dropship", Set To, 1);
	Set Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Battlecruiser", Set To, 0);
	Set Switch("Switch7", set);
}

//-----------------------------------------------------------------//

Trigger("Player 1"){
Conditions:
	Bring("Player 4", "Terran Ghost", "Anywhere", Exactly, 0);

Actions:
	Preserve Trigger();
	Create Unit("Player 4", "Terran Ghost", 1, "7x7");
}

//-----------------------------------------------------------------//

Trigger("Player 1"){
Conditions:
	Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Science Vessel", Exactly, 0);
	Bring("Player 9", "Zerg Zergling", "Selection Area", At least, 1);

Actions:
	Preserve Trigger();
	Move Location("Player 9", "Zerg Zergling", "Selection Area", "7x7");
	Move Location("Player 1", "Map Revealer", "7x7", "12x12");
	Move Location("Player 1", "Zerg Zergling", "7x7", "1x1 Pixel");
	Move Unit("Player 4", "Terran Ghost", All, "Anywhere", "1x1 Pixel");
}

//-----------------------------------------------------------------//

Trigger("Player 1"){
Conditions:
	Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Science Vessel", Exactly, 0);
	Bring("Player 9", "Zerg Zergling", "Selection Area", At least, 1);
	Bring("Player 4", "Terran Ghost", "1x1 Pixel", Exactly, 1);
	Bring("Player 1", "Zerg Zergling", "7x7", Exactly, 1);

Actions:
	Preserve Trigger();
	Set Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Science Vessel", Set To, 1);
	Set Deaths("Player 8", "Gui Montag (Firebat)", Set To, 1);
}

	Set Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Battlecruiser", Set To, 0);

	Move Unit("Player 9", "Unclean One (Defiler)", All, "7x7", "7x7");
	Move Location("Player 11", "Infested Terran", "Yu1", "Xshift");
	Move Location("Player 1", "Map Revealer", "Xshift", "X119");

	Center View("G0,0");
}

	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G0,0", 1);
	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G4,0", 1);
	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G0,1", 1);
	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G4,1", 1);
	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G0,2", 1);
	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G4,2", 1);
	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G1,3", 1);
	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G2,3", 1);
	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G3,3", 1);
	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G4,3", 1);
	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G4,4", 1);
	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G4,5", 1);
	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G2,6", 1);
	Create Unit with Properties("Player 8", "Devouring One (Zergling)", 1, "G3,6", 1);
	Set Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Vulture", Add, 7);
}

Trigger("All Players"){
Conditions:
	Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Marine", Exactly, 3);

Actions:
	Preserve Trigger();
	Set Deaths("Player 8", "Alan Schezar (Goliath)", Add, 1);
	Set Switch("Switch1", clear);
	Set Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Vulture", Set To, 0);
	Set Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Goliath", Set To, 0);
}

//-----------------------------------------------------------------//

Trigger("All Players"){
Conditions:
	Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Marine", Exactly, 10);

Actions:
	Preserve Trigger();
	Set Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Goliath", Add, 10);
	Set Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Vulture", Set To, 0);
	Set Deaths("Player 8", "Terran Wraith", Set To, 0);
}
